      <title>代理劳工部长苏称 6 月份就业报告“稳健”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/acting-labor-secretary-su-calls-june-jobs-report-solid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国代理劳工部长朱莉·苏表示，6 月份美国就业报告显示经济“强劲、稳定”。美国劳工统计局称，上个月非农就业人数增加了 20.6 万，而前两个月的就业增长被下调了 11.1 万。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/acting-labor-secretary-su-calls-june-jobs-report-solid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:13:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>益普索预测勒庞将在法国大选中赢得 175-205 个席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-projected-to-win-175-205-seats-in-french-vote-ipsos-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[益普索 (Ipsos) 对 10,101 名登记选民的调查显示，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟及其盟友预计将在周日的法国立法议会选举中赢得 175 至 205 个席位，远低于获得多数席位所需的 289 个席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-projected-to-win-175-205-seats-in-french-vote-ipsos-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:06:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管美国封闭式基金行业遭遇困境，但比尔·阿克曼仍押注该行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bill-ackman-bets-on-us-closed-end-fund-despite-lean-years-for-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼已经习惯了漫长而艰难的维权运动。说服散户投资者将约 250 亿美元投资于他自己的美国封闭式基金可能又是一场艰苦的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bill-ackman-bets-on-us-closed-end-fund-despite-lean-years-for-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
